com.ibm.team.build.common.model

Interface IBuildDefinitionInstance


  • public interface IBuildDefinitionInstance
    Represents a snapshot of a build definition at the moment the build request is made to preserve the state of that build definition to be used when the request is processed.
    Since:
    0.5
